<h1 >News List or Grid</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="041c04e9-e8ac-4d59-9269-8bc48051b2fa" >

    <p>The News list/grid component allows users to create a list or grid (with images) of news stories.</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>This component must be used with the following templates:<br> 
  <ul> 
   <li><a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/responsive-templates/news-template.html">News template</a></li> 
   <li>News release pages must be created before they can be displayed in the news list or grid.</li> 
   <li>News releases must be created in a <a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/responsive-templates/archive-template.html">Yearly Archive template</a></li> 
  </ul> </li> 
</ul> 
<ul> 
 <li>Found in Sidekick&gt; Lists and Grids&gt;News</li> 
 <li>Display options: List display and Grid view 
  <ul> 
   <li>Thumbnails are not displayed in the list style.</li> 
   <li>Thumbnails added to the news release template will display in Grid display only.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li>Custom Colours Applicable:&nbsp; No&nbsp;&nbsp;</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#041c04e9-e8ac-4d59-9269-8bc48051b2fa");});</script></div>

				

				
