<div class="restext_1017326843 resText parbase">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="b2b660e8-dacf-4c94-8197-a7f6eea96009" >

    <p><strong> List Filtering Options:</strong></p> 
<p>"Autocategorized Tags" and "Categorized Tags" are two filtering options which allow users to filter list results using one or more tags. <a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/components/lists-grids/list-filtering-by-tags.html">Learn how to use tag filtering</a>.</p>
    





</div>
